  (AI agents are the consumer). Agent Sessions = human session browser + Agent
  Cockpit HUD + resume (not MCP); ReadOut = AI-native chat dashboard with
  data-card embeds + one-click actions (not MCP). Defensible: 17-source breadth
  (Swift parity-tested), project-migration path repair (no competitor has it),
  cross-tool parent-child grouping, encrypted opt-in remote offload,
  vendor-neutral zero-telemetry.
