## 2026-06-06 — Claude/Qoder grouped-dir reconcile for historical project moves (Codex)

Codex added startup repair for already-orphaned Claude Code/Qoder grouped
project directories left behind by earlier runs that used the incomplete
directory encoder.

Change:
- Swift startup maintenance calls `GroupedDirReconcile.run(roots:
  SessionSources.roots())` after insight reconciliation and before file-path
  backfill. It emits a `db_maintenance` event with scanned/planned/applied,
  collision, ambiguous, and issue counts when there is work or a warning.
- The reconcile scanner is intentionally scoped to `.claude/projects` and
  `.qoder/projects`. It extracts structured `cwd` values from JSON/JSONL
  session files and computes the corrected Claude/Qoder directory name.
- Repair uses no-overwrite copy/delete semantics rather than blind rename, so
  existing target directories become collisions and the source directory is
  left in place.
- Safety guards skip child symlinks, nested symlink evidence, ambiguous
  directories, missing roots, already-correct directories, target collisions,
  and session files above the 50 MiB structured-cwd read cap.
- A TypeScript reference helper in `src/core/project-move/grouped-dir-reconcile.ts`
  mirrors the same behavior for parity tests and future migrations.

Review:
- Plan review initially returned CHANGES_REQUESTED for no-overwrite races,
  symlink coverage, startup ordering, Qoder parity, and wording mismatches.
  The plan/spec were patched before implementation.
- Implementation review initially returned CHANGES_REQUESTED because the new
  scanner did not apply the existing 50 MiB structured-cwd read cap. Codex
  added Swift/TS cap tests and implementation; the follow-up review returned
  PASS.

Verification:
- RED oversized-file tests failed before the cap fix in both TS and Swift.
- `npx vitest run tests/core/project-move/grouped-dir-reconcile.test.ts -t
  "skips oversized files"` passed.
- `xcodebuild test -project macos/Engram.xcodeproj -scheme EngramCoreTests
  -destination 'platform=macOS'
  -only-testing:EngramCoreTests/SessionSourcesTests/testGroupedDirReconcileSkipsOversizedFiles
  CODE_SIGNING_ALLOWED=NO` passed.
- `npx biome check src/core/project-move/grouped-dir-reconcile.ts
  tests/core/project-move/grouped-dir-reconcile.test.ts` passed.
- `npx vitest run tests/core/project-move/grouped-dir-reconcile.test.ts
  tests/core/project-move/encode-cc.test.ts
  tests/core/project-move/orchestrator.integration.test.ts` passed 49 tests.
- `xcodebuild test -project macos/Engram.xcodeproj -scheme EngramCoreTests
  -destination 'platform=macOS' -only-testing:EngramCoreTests/SessionSourcesTests
  -only-testing:EngramCoreTests/StartupBackfillTests
  -only-testing:EngramCoreTests/OrchestratorTests CODE_SIGNING_ALLOWED=NO`
  passed 78 tests.
