- `xcodebuild test -project macos/Engram.xcodeproj -scheme EngramServiceCore -destination 'platform=macOS' CODE_SIGNING_ALLOWED=NO` initially exposed the unisolated HOME/AI-settings test issue, then passed after the isolation fix: 127 tests.
- `xcodebuild test -project macos/Engram.xcodeproj -scheme EngramTests -destination 'platform=macOS' CODE_SIGNING_ALLOWED=NO` passed: 299 tests, 1 skipped.

